      "content": "You just said the lack of intrinsic factor leads to impaired absorption, but doesn't the lack of the *vitamin itself* in a plant-based diet cause the deficiency? Also, you mentioned something about the body \"relying on the stomach\" to produce the protein, which doesn't quite make sense—the protein is produced regardless of what you eat. Can you clarify why the absence of B12 in certain diets is such a major issue for the absorption pathway you described?",
